    meta:     '[Stack] · [Year]',
    body: [
      'Placeholder — a third development project. By this point you have shown range. This project can be a specialisation: something deep in one area — a complex UI interaction, a performance optimisation, an unusual integration, or a data visualisation.',
      'What skill does this project demonstrate that the others do not? What would someone reading this understand about your engineering approach that they would not know from the first two projects?',
      'Update with your actual project. Remove all placeholder text. Be specific about the stack, the problem, and the outcome. Vague descriptions do not build trust with technical readers.',
    ],
    topics: ['The Specialisation', 'What It Proves', 'Be Specific'],
  },
  {
    id:       'open-source',
    category: 'OPEN SOURCE',
